<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Brand Landing Page Sample</title>
  <style>
    /* Font Imports for DM Sans and serif fallback */
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:wght@700&display=swap');
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Merriweather&display=swap');

    /* Color Palette from stylebook */
    :root {
      --burgundy-brown: #912D29;
      --butter-cream: #F9E49D;
      --ivory: #FEF7E7;
      --cobalt-blue: #2871B5;
      --light-blue: #9CBDD8;
      --christmas-green: #1C5630;
      --blush-pink: #E8A1B0;
      --text-dark: #3A3A3A;
      --text-light: #fff;
    }

    /* Reset and base styles */
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Merriweather', serif;
      background-color: var(--butter-cream);
      color: var(--text-dark);
      line-height: 1.6;
      padding: 2rem;
    }

    h1, h2, h3 {
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      color: var(--burgundy-brown);
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    p {
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
      font-size: 1.125rem;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: auto;
      background-color: var(--ivory);
      padding: 2rem 3rem;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    .button-primary {
      background-color: var(--burgundy-brown);
      color: var(--butter-cream);
      border: none;
      padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 1.125rem;
      border-radius: 5px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 1rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .button-primary:hover {
      background-color: var(--cobalt-blue);
    }

    .intro {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      font-family: 'Merriweather', serif;
      font-style: italic;
      color: var(--christmas-green);
    }

    .feature {
      border-left: 6px solid var(--blush-pink);
      padding-left: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem;
      color: var(--text-dark);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      margin-top: 3rem;
    }

  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="container">
    <h1>Welcome to Drippi Coffee</h1>
    <p class="intro">Elevate your morning ritual with premium, lovingly crafted coffee moments.</p>

    <h2>Our Promise</h2>
    <p>Discover the rich flavors of sustainable, freshly roasted coffee delivered with care and passion. Whether you savor a quiet moment or share with friends, Drippi brings calm and joy to your day.</p>

    <div class="feature">
      <h3>Premium Quality</h3>
      <p>Only the finest beans, roasted to perfection and delivered fresh.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature">
      <h3>Thoughtful Rituals</h3>
      <p>Every cup brewed with intention for your calm, mindful mornings.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature">
      <h3>A Warm Community</h3>
      <p>Join fellow coffee lovers who cherish connection and quality.</p>
    </div>

    <a href="#shop" class="button-primary">Shop Now</a>
  </div>

  <footer>
    &copy; 2026 Drippi Coffee. All rights reserved.
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
